{
  "stem": "3097.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because like, you have to deal with smart people, and the subjects, and I think the schools in Poland-- high schools-- were on a high-- much higher level than United States, you see.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was not too much for social life at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as far as-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I did observe a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Except I personally, as a kid in school, could observe only those things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Like, you know, bombs, and stink bombs, placards, 'don't buy here,' destroying the [? stands ?] on a-- a-- a street.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And all those things then I did observe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was born in Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I thought to be a citizen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I spoke Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I dressed the way they did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I walked the way they did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I sounded-- I spoke a perfect Polish without any accent.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I spoke even slang-- Polish slang-- which helped me in the forest and with the peasants.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they did recognize me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They knew that I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By looking at me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the biggest tragedy in Poland was that some of the people who German did not recognize as Jews were on the Aryan side.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Teenagers, Poles, did point out to the Germans the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If that would be not the fact, thousands and thousands more would survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[CRYING] I get emotional because my aunt and my cousin were killed [SOBBING] by the-- by the Poles.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We-- I-- I listened to the radio.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had the radio.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I did even listen to the Russian radio.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had a big radio, [INAUDIBLE], [INAUDIBLE], they used to call it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], you see.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
